"     </b>",
"     (Zerit Oral)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     1 mg/mL (200 mL): $102.73",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F222995\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Monitor liver function tests and renal function tests; signs and symptoms of peripheral neuropathy; monitor viral load and CD4 count",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"list fbnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F223010\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
